WEBVTT

00:17.000 --> 00:19.640
-What's wrong?
-Stop.

00:19.720 --> 00:21.080
-Say that again.
-Enough.

00:21.160 --> 00:22.400
-Say that again.
-Step back.

00:22.480 --> 00:24.080
Enough. Step back.

00:24.880 --> 00:25.880
Let them go this once.

00:26.920 --> 00:28.080
Those prisoners,

00:28.160 --> 00:30.080
our Yanzhou army shed blood
and sweat to capture them.

00:30.600 --> 00:32.400
What right do you Jizhou troops have
to take half?

00:32.479 --> 00:34.360
-Exactly.
-What right do you have?

00:34.440 --> 00:35.120
What right?

00:35.200 --> 00:38.360
Captain Fan and our Military Administrator
are deeply in love.

00:38.440 --> 00:40.480
-Right.
-Soon they'll be family.

00:40.560 --> 00:42.400
Half?

00:42.920 --> 00:44.680
You should give us all of them.

00:44.760 --> 00:46.280
It's only right.

00:46.360 --> 00:47.400
-Exactly.
-Only right.

00:47.480 --> 00:48.680
Shut up!

00:49.400 --> 00:50.240
Nonsense!

00:50.960 --> 00:53.200
Captain Fan already has a husband.

00:53.280 --> 00:56.000
How could she possibly fool around with
Military Administrator Li behind his back?

00:56.080 --> 00:57.480
Bullshit!

00:57.560 --> 01:00.760
Captain Fan's husband died
on the battlefield long ago.

01:01.280 --> 01:02.480
Even if he were alive,

01:02.560 --> 01:05.720
how could he compare
to our Military Administrator?

01:05.800 --> 01:07.000
Exactly.

01:07.080 --> 01:10.520
Wait. Isn't your Military Administrator Li
supposed to marry the Grand Princess?

01:10.600 --> 01:12.440
So why's he tangled up with Captain Fan?

01:12.520 --> 01:15.000
-Exactly.
-None of your damn business.

01:15.080 --> 01:17.280
Our Military Administrator visits
Captain Fan every single day. So what?

01:17.360 --> 01:19.040
You, on the other hand,

01:19.120 --> 01:20.840
could it be that your master

01:21.360 --> 01:22.720
has his eye on Captain Fan too?

01:22.800 --> 01:23.960
-Bullshit!
-What did you say?

01:24.040 --> 01:24.840
You got a problem?

01:24.920 --> 01:26.400
-Then fight.
-Why did you strike first?

01:27.160 --> 01:28.360
-Stop it!
-Let go.

01:28.440 --> 01:29.760
-Attention!
-Watch yourselves.

01:29.840 --> 01:32.040
PEACE AND PROSPERITY ALONG THE BORDERS

01:32.120 --> 01:33.400
We're all brothers in arms,

01:34.200 --> 01:36.160
yet you fight and injure
each other over prisoners.

01:36.880 --> 01:37.800
Where are the military regulations?

01:38.760 --> 01:41.360
Lord Li, you be the judge.

01:41.440 --> 01:43.800
You and Captain Fan
are practically family now.

01:44.400 --> 01:46.920
Why split the military merits so clearly?

01:47.000 --> 01:48.000
How dare you!

01:49.000 --> 01:51.080
Such gossip shouldn't
be spoken carelessly.

01:51.160 --> 01:53.200
I don't care if Military Administrator Li
likes Captain Fan or not.

01:53.280 --> 01:55.520
But taking away the military merits of our
Yanzhou warriors?

01:55.600 --> 01:56.480
That's not acceptable.

01:56.560 --> 01:57.880
-Right?
-So what?

01:57.960 --> 02:00.360
-You got a problem?
-Don't you?

02:00.440 --> 02:01.440
All troops, hear my command!

02:01.520 --> 02:02.360
TOKEN

02:05.840 --> 02:07.680
Captain Fan and I have known
each other since we were nothing.

02:08.280 --> 02:09.600
Just like all of you,

02:10.120 --> 02:12.040
we share the bond of fighting
side by side, of life and death.

02:12.680 --> 02:16.400
Today, Captain Fan and I have sworn
to be brother and sister.

02:17.400 --> 02:18.640
From now on,

02:18.720 --> 02:20.480
I will treat her as my own sister.

02:21.800 --> 02:25.000
If anyone dares to spread rumors,
stir up trouble,

02:25.760 --> 02:27.640
or slander Captain Fan's honor again,

02:28.160 --> 02:30.800
they will receive 30 strokes
of the military cane, as a warning to all.

02:30.880 --> 02:31.720
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

02:40.440 --> 02:41.360
Let's go.

02:50.160 --> 02:51.000
Captain Fan.

02:51.080 --> 02:52.680
YAMEN

02:55.360 --> 02:56.360
You all go ahead.

02:57.920 --> 02:58.760
Let's go.

03:03.840 --> 03:05.280
Just now, calling you my sister,

03:05.360 --> 03:06.480
that was only a temporary measure.

03:06.560 --> 03:08.280
There are gossips in the army.

03:08.360 --> 03:10.480
If it offended you,
please don't take it to heart.

03:11.360 --> 03:12.360
How could I?

03:12.880 --> 03:15.040
I've always considered you
as an elder brother.

03:15.720 --> 03:16.960
I'm just afraid I don't deserve.

03:17.040 --> 03:20.080
After all, I've barely read
any military books,

03:20.600 --> 03:21.720
and I hardly know characters.

03:23.600 --> 03:25.600
The way to know a person
lies in their inner qualities.

03:25.680 --> 03:26.920
It has nothing to do
with reading or literacy.

03:27.880 --> 03:31.320
Then as your sister,
I pay my courtesy to you, my brother.

03:32.480 --> 03:33.400
Is that how it's said?

03:38.120 --> 03:40.320
I hereby return the greetings.
That's how it's said.

03:41.440 --> 03:42.560
Then I'll take my leave now.

05:26.280 --> 05:30.360
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

05:33.160 --> 05:34.880
HALL OF ARMS

05:34.960 --> 05:36.920
This is absolutely outrageous!

05:37.720 --> 05:39.400
Even in the palace,

05:39.480 --> 05:41.960
I've never been treated
with such disrespect.

05:46.240 --> 05:47.120
What are you doing?

05:47.200 --> 05:49.600
You still expect me to drink this?

05:49.680 --> 05:51.360
No. It's been days now.

05:52.800 --> 05:55.000
The Marquis of Wu'an hasn't returned,

05:55.080 --> 05:57.000
and the Grand Princess won't see me.

05:57.800 --> 05:58.960
Let me tell you.

05:59.480 --> 06:02.840
If you keep me
waiting here like this today,

06:02.920 --> 06:05.560
I will immediately
set out for the capital.

06:05.640 --> 06:08.760
I'll go before His Majesty.
I'll file an imperial complaint.

06:11.120 --> 06:12.360
What's all this commotion?

06:14.880 --> 06:18.240
Greetings to the Grand Princess.

06:19.840 --> 06:21.760
Your Highness cares
so deeply for the soldiers

06:21.840 --> 06:22.760
that you haven't found a moment

06:22.840 --> 06:25.320
to see me all these days.

06:25.400 --> 06:27.600
How truly touching.

06:27.680 --> 06:28.600
You may go.

06:31.400 --> 06:32.960
I've been overwhelmed with affairs lately,

06:33.040 --> 06:34.920
truly unable to spare a moment.

06:35.000 --> 06:36.480
I hope you'll understand.

06:37.600 --> 06:40.880
May I ask why you've sought me out?

06:40.960 --> 06:43.000
Your Highness has been away
from the palace for quite some time.

06:43.080 --> 06:46.760
His Majesty and Empress Dowager An
are deeply concerned.

06:46.840 --> 06:50.480
So they specially sent me to come
and see how the Grand Princess is faring.

06:52.840 --> 06:54.360
Mother and His Majesty

06:54.880 --> 06:57.040
know that I am here,
at the northwest front,

06:57.920 --> 06:59.160
and yet they're not angry?

07:02.920 --> 07:04.640
Eunuch, you may as well speak directly.

07:05.800 --> 07:07.920
Your Highness is remarkably perceptive.

07:08.000 --> 07:10.120
Indeed, before I came,

07:10.200 --> 07:15.000
His Majesty and Empress Dowager An
specially asked me

07:15.080 --> 07:17.800
to convey a message to Your Highness,

07:18.960 --> 07:22.760
"Now that the Chongzhou rebels
have been pacified,

07:22.840 --> 07:25.000
as the whole nation celebrates,

07:25.600 --> 07:27.600
this marriage between you and the Marquis,

07:27.680 --> 07:30.560
-it's better sooner than later."
-What did you say?

07:31.760 --> 07:33.600
My marriage to whom?

07:35.160 --> 07:36.800
The Marquis of Wu'an.

07:37.320 --> 07:38.280
Preposterous!

07:40.160 --> 07:41.320
My imperial brother is easily swayed.

07:42.200 --> 07:45.040
It must be you foolish servants,
dredging up old matters

07:45.120 --> 07:47.880
and fanning the flames,
that put this idea in his head.

07:48.400 --> 07:51.040
This marriage, I do not accept it.

07:54.920 --> 07:57.320
Your Highness, you left the palace
for less than six months.

07:57.400 --> 08:00.680
Since when did you learn to curse?

08:04.040 --> 08:05.840
The Marquis of Wu'an has earned
great distinction in battle.

08:05.920 --> 08:09.080
By any measure,
he's a match of the highest order.

08:09.920 --> 08:14.080
Besides, this is His Majesty's decree.

08:14.160 --> 08:15.520
Surely you're not thinking of…

08:16.280 --> 08:18.680
defying an imperial order?

08:30.480 --> 08:31.880
This marriage,

08:32.480 --> 08:34.880
you'd better take it up
with the Marquis of Wu'an first.

08:36.000 --> 08:37.159
If he agrees,

08:37.919 --> 08:39.200
then I'll agree.

08:42.240 --> 08:43.960
Easy enough.

08:45.080 --> 08:47.560
I'll see to it right away.

08:55.400 --> 08:57.720
Please convey this to His Majesty for me.

08:58.520 --> 08:59.600
I am grateful…

09:00.640 --> 09:02.840
for my imperial brother's care.

09:02.920 --> 09:06.000
I'll take my leave now.

09:15.440 --> 09:17.160
Finally got that off my chest.

09:20.040 --> 09:21.720
HE

09:23.720 --> 09:25.960
It's been days now.

09:26.480 --> 09:30.360
Busy or not, the Marquis
can't keep an imperial decree waiting.

09:31.360 --> 09:33.200
This is a military camp. Please stop here.

09:36.040 --> 09:37.200
Fine.

09:37.720 --> 09:40.600
Open your worthless eyes wide
and look clearly!

09:40.680 --> 09:42.840
I have the imperial decree right here!

09:44.600 --> 09:48.000
Let's see who dares to stop me today!

09:49.680 --> 09:50.560
Let's go.

09:58.000 --> 09:59.120
Stop.

10:01.320 --> 10:03.920
I know the Marquis
is busy with official duties.

10:04.000 --> 10:05.560
But these past few days,

10:05.640 --> 10:09.520
you haven't found a moment to see me.

10:09.600 --> 10:12.840
Left with no choice,
I've brought the imperial decree

10:12.920 --> 10:16.280
and come to trouble you here myself.

10:18.920 --> 10:19.760
Come in.

10:24.200 --> 10:25.040
Please.

10:33.160 --> 10:35.720
I pay my respect to the Marquis.

10:39.720 --> 10:41.320
What urgent matter
brings you here, Eunuch?

10:42.440 --> 10:43.800
And daring to enter a military camp

10:44.320 --> 10:46.000
without authorization just to see me?

10:49.600 --> 10:53.680
Marquis, this is tremendous good news!

10:56.960 --> 10:59.240
His Majesty has issued a decree.

11:04.080 --> 11:04.960
Marquis of Wu'an…

11:10.520 --> 11:13.080
The Marquis need not kneel to hear it.

11:14.600 --> 11:17.400
His Imperial Majesty decrees,
"Heaven blesses our dynasty.

11:17.480 --> 11:20.680
Now that the Chongzhou rebels
have been vanquished

11:20.760 --> 11:23.880
and the nation rejoices,

11:23.960 --> 11:27.200
the marriage between the Grand Princess
and the Marquis of Wu'an should be

11:27.280 --> 11:29.800
-concluded sooner rather than later."
-Eunuch, say no more.

11:30.400 --> 11:32.160
Go back and tell the young emperor

11:32.840 --> 11:34.560
that urgent matters prevent the Marquis

11:35.080 --> 11:36.520
from receiving the decree.

11:36.600 --> 11:39.560
Consider today's words never spoken.

11:40.560 --> 11:44.080
And no one else here
will breathe a word of it.

11:45.680 --> 11:49.600
I wouldn't dare commit such an act
of deceiving the emperor.

11:50.320 --> 11:55.720
Besides, this is His Majesty's favor
toward you, Marquis.

11:55.800 --> 11:59.040
Just nod once, that's all it takes,

11:59.120 --> 12:03.680
and I can return to the capital
and report back to His Majesty.

12:05.320 --> 12:06.720
But if I…

12:08.080 --> 12:09.560
refuse to nod?

12:10.840 --> 12:12.160
Refuse…

12:14.200 --> 12:19.080
Marquis, are you saying
you'd defy the decree?

12:19.920 --> 12:22.760
I wouldn't dare deceive the emperor.

12:24.640 --> 12:25.480
Defy the decree?

12:33.160 --> 12:35.760
Marquis. What do you think you're doing?

12:41.960 --> 12:43.080
Marquis of Wu'an…

12:43.600 --> 12:47.040
Are you really plotting rebellion?

12:53.680 --> 12:57.200
The Xie family has served Dayin
loyally for a hundred years.

12:58.560 --> 13:00.600
My father even earned the title of martyr.

13:02.480 --> 13:04.680
I simply don't want to tarnish his name.

13:08.680 --> 13:10.560
Go back and tell the young emperor,

13:11.560 --> 13:13.480
if he doesn't want to sit on that throne,

13:14.200 --> 13:16.280
I can easily find someone else
to take his place.

13:16.880 --> 13:18.320
Seventeen years ago,

13:18.400 --> 13:20.320
Wei Yan helped him onto the dragon throne.

13:21.600 --> 13:22.760
Today,

13:23.720 --> 13:25.600
I can easily pull him down.

13:26.440 --> 13:28.040
What?

13:28.600 --> 13:29.480
Marquis of Wu'an,

13:30.000 --> 13:32.760
do you realize
you're threatening His Majesty?

13:35.400 --> 13:37.320
Please, Marquis, don't kill me.

13:37.400 --> 13:40.800
I'm just a messenger for the decree.

13:48.040 --> 13:52.320
I merely wish for harmony
between ruler and subject.

13:53.440 --> 13:55.680
If you misreport my words,

13:57.120 --> 13:58.760
don't let it jeopardize matters of state.

14:00.640 --> 14:01.520
Thank you.

14:02.040 --> 14:05.240
Thank you, Marquis, for sparing my life.

14:15.880 --> 14:17.360
-It's…
-Take it yourself.

14:28.120 --> 14:29.200
Leave quickly!

14:29.920 --> 14:32.080
Be gentle.

14:33.520 --> 14:35.520
ARMED AND UNYIELDING

14:43.360 --> 14:45.160
Xie Jiuheng.

14:45.840 --> 14:48.600
Eunuch Li came here on imperial orders.

14:48.680 --> 14:51.800
Cutting off his ear… That's practically
slapping the emperor in the face.

14:51.880 --> 14:53.280
What now?

14:53.960 --> 14:54.920
Are we picking a fight with the court?

14:57.280 --> 14:59.440
The young emperor
is still playing the fool

14:59.520 --> 15:01.000
under Wei Yan's thumb.

15:01.080 --> 15:02.480
Does he dare pick a fight with me?

15:05.960 --> 15:07.960
His Majesty sits at the throne
since he was a child.

15:08.040 --> 15:10.320
He has his authority usurped
by Chancellor Wei all these years.

15:10.400 --> 15:13.200
By now, he must be desperate for power.

15:13.280 --> 15:15.400
I don't think he'll let this slide.

15:16.000 --> 15:18.040
If he doesn't want to sit on that throne,

15:18.120 --> 15:19.560
I can find someone else to take his place.

15:20.800 --> 15:21.960
As it happens, I have been

15:23.080 --> 15:24.680
considering deposing the emperor.

15:27.080 --> 15:28.160
Depose the emperor?

15:29.200 --> 15:30.040
Are you serious?

15:38.040 --> 15:42.360
I know the Dayin court
is too muddy to look at.

15:43.040 --> 15:45.640
I know you don't want to serve
such a worthless ruler.

15:46.400 --> 15:47.240
But if

15:47.920 --> 15:50.400
we support the imperial grandson now,
give it a decade or two,

15:50.480 --> 15:53.880
who's to say Yu Bao'er
won't turn into another Qi Sheng?

15:58.320 --> 16:00.360
What Yu Bao'er becomes in the future,

16:00.440 --> 16:01.440
I don't know.

16:02.360 --> 16:04.720
But I will never become another Wei Yan.

16:08.280 --> 16:10.280
Alright. By the way,

16:11.080 --> 16:12.280
aren't you heading back to Jizhou Yamen?

16:13.040 --> 16:13.880
What for?

16:15.880 --> 16:19.080
That Li Huai'an
keeps visiting Mrs. Fan every other day.

16:19.160 --> 16:20.600
You're really not worried?

16:25.200 --> 16:26.760
Don't look at me like that.

16:27.280 --> 16:29.920
They've already started calling each other
brother and sister, building rapport.

16:30.000 --> 16:32.440
And when she's vulnerable,
he'll seize the opportunity.

16:32.520 --> 16:34.360
-The most basic courtship tactic--
-Enough.

16:34.880 --> 16:36.720
-You're the advanced one. Happy?
-I…

16:36.800 --> 16:37.640
Mind your own business.

16:38.240 --> 16:39.160
Report!

16:40.600 --> 16:41.760
Marquis,

16:41.840 --> 16:44.240
Sui Yuanqing, with the remaining enemy
from Chongzhou, is attacking us.

16:52.200 --> 16:53.320
How many troops?

16:53.400 --> 16:54.960
Just a few dozen soldiers,

16:55.040 --> 16:57.600
charging the gate like madmen,
with no reinforcements behind them.

16:57.680 --> 16:59.640
Looks like they're here to die.

17:06.680 --> 17:08.280
Xie Zheng!

17:09.200 --> 17:11.599
Come out, you coward!

17:12.720 --> 17:15.800
Let's settle this today.

17:33.800 --> 17:35.640
Why put yourself through this, Young Heir?

17:36.200 --> 17:37.640
Why come all this way just to die?

17:40.920 --> 17:42.680
Save your false pity.

17:43.280 --> 17:45.520
You and Fan Changyu killed my father.

17:46.360 --> 17:47.720
If I don't avenge him,

17:48.480 --> 17:49.720
I'm not fit to live.

17:50.480 --> 17:51.880
Prepare to die!

18:10.520 --> 18:14.040
CHONGZHOU

18:14.640 --> 18:16.560
If he believes it, fine.

18:16.640 --> 18:17.640
If not,

18:18.680 --> 18:20.600
destroy the Eastern Palace seal
on the spot.

18:20.680 --> 18:22.640
It must never fall
into anyone else's hands.

18:23.160 --> 18:24.040
Rest assured, Master.

18:30.280 --> 18:32.200
LADY YIN, PRINCESS CHANGXIN

18:34.800 --> 18:35.640
Mother?

18:42.080 --> 18:42.960
What brings you here so suddenly?

18:44.360 --> 18:46.240
Why do you treat your brother this way?

18:50.240 --> 18:53.520
Yuanqing said he wanted to avenge Father.

18:54.320 --> 18:57.040
That's filial piety. I couldn't stop him.

18:57.120 --> 18:58.200
Filial piety?

18:58.280 --> 19:00.360
Then why don't you go fulfill it yourself?

19:02.360 --> 19:04.720
I have to stay
and take care of you, Mother.

19:05.600 --> 19:08.640
You knew perfectly well the Marquis
of Wu'an is hunting you everywhere.

19:09.440 --> 19:11.520
Yet you still stirred up Yuanqing
to avenge the prince.

19:11.600 --> 19:12.680
How vicious.

19:20.200 --> 19:22.280
Father never liked me.

19:23.880 --> 19:25.440
And in your heart,

19:26.320 --> 19:27.800
you always preferred
Yuanqing too, didn't you?

19:28.840 --> 19:29.800
He's my son.

19:30.440 --> 19:31.560
Of course I prefer him.

19:37.360 --> 19:38.280
Mother,

19:39.840 --> 19:41.040
what do you mean by that?

19:42.040 --> 19:43.200
What mother

19:44.440 --> 19:47.240
doesn't recognize her own child?

19:50.960 --> 19:53.440
After that fire 17 years ago,

19:53.960 --> 19:55.520
I brought you back.

19:57.800 --> 19:58.960
At first,

20:00.000 --> 20:02.440
seeing you so disfigured, my heart ached.

20:03.920 --> 20:07.520
But when I learned you weren't Yuanhuai,
my heart ached even more.

20:12.600 --> 20:14.040
So you knew all along.

20:18.360 --> 20:19.320
Then,

20:19.960 --> 20:21.880
why didn't you expose me
right then and there?

20:22.480 --> 20:23.520
You were just

20:24.200 --> 20:25.800
a small child then,

20:27.280 --> 20:30.160
disfigured by the Crown Princess
just to stay alive.

20:31.120 --> 20:33.480
While recovering in Changxin Manor,

20:33.560 --> 20:35.520
you were so pitiful,

20:36.040 --> 20:38.440
crying every day for your mother.

20:39.080 --> 20:41.360
It softened my heart.

20:42.520 --> 20:43.440
I thought,

20:44.560 --> 20:48.480
since heaven let you live
in my son's place, then let you live well.

20:50.600 --> 20:54.000
Consider it good karma for my Yuanhuai,
who died poorly and unjustly.

20:55.880 --> 20:57.600
But I was wrong.

20:58.640 --> 21:00.520
I thought you were just a lost dog.

21:00.600 --> 21:02.520
Never imagined you were a starving wolf.

21:04.160 --> 21:05.880
The greatest regret of my life

21:06.520 --> 21:08.120
is taking a viper for a son,

21:08.920 --> 21:11.040
becoming a mother to someone so venomous.

21:21.160 --> 21:26.880
I am Qi Min, the Crown Prince's grandson
of the Eastern Palace.

21:34.000 --> 21:36.040
Isn't being my mother

21:38.080 --> 21:38.960
good enough for you?

21:44.360 --> 21:45.600
I only have

21:46.320 --> 21:48.640
Yuanqing and Yuanhuai as my sons.

21:50.160 --> 21:51.000
You…

21:51.920 --> 21:53.040
didn't deserve it!

22:33.120 --> 22:34.600
Don't think that just because
you were kind to me,

22:35.840 --> 22:37.520
I wouldn't dare kill you.

22:42.240 --> 22:44.440
I… I gave you a chance.

22:47.840 --> 22:49.160
But don't worry.

22:50.440 --> 22:54.200
Xie Zheng will soon send Sui Yuanqing

22:54.280 --> 22:56.120
to your side to fulfill his filial duty.

23:24.480 --> 23:27.960
-Take her body. It might still be useful.
-Yes, sir.

23:36.800 --> 23:39.960
HE

23:46.960 --> 23:48.200
Come in.

23:53.000 --> 23:53.840
Fan,

23:54.600 --> 23:56.840
is it true your husband's going to be
the prince consort?

23:59.440 --> 24:01.080
I thought Li Menkan
was marrying the princess.

24:01.160 --> 24:03.680
Swapping grooms at the last minute
for something this big? Really?

24:04.760 --> 24:05.840
I don't want to talk about this.

24:11.080 --> 24:11.920
Alright.

24:17.920 --> 24:20.440
You asked me to look into Sui Yuanhuai.
I found something.

24:22.400 --> 24:25.200
Word is, tonight
they're sending out a large force.

24:25.280 --> 24:27.480
Probably a massive manhunt
for that bastard.

24:28.760 --> 24:31.080
That traitor's crafty,

24:31.600 --> 24:33.280
slyer than a fox, sneakier than a weasel.

24:33.360 --> 24:34.720
Even the troops your husband…

24:37.880 --> 24:39.800
I mean Marquis of Wu'an

24:40.320 --> 24:42.200
sent before, he's fooled them
multiple times.

24:44.720 --> 24:46.000
He's muddying the waters.

24:47.360 --> 24:50.600
When we're tired of searching,
he'll slip away.

24:54.080 --> 24:56.360
So he's the son of some crown prince?

24:56.440 --> 24:57.520
He could've…

24:58.960 --> 25:00.080
could've been the emperor?

25:01.880 --> 25:03.280
He could have been, once.

25:06.480 --> 25:08.720
If he was so noble,

25:09.720 --> 25:12.160
why would he pretend to be Sui Yuanhuai?

25:13.160 --> 25:15.440
You've watched plenty of puppet plays.
You see it all the time, don't you?

25:16.040 --> 25:18.880
Those nobles and lords,
scheming and fighting day in and day out.

25:19.400 --> 25:22.520
It's all just greed for the throne
and the power, like flies after meat.

25:29.840 --> 25:31.000
Fan, what are you looking at?

25:33.200 --> 25:34.600
Qian once said

25:35.120 --> 25:36.920
he's terrified of fire,

25:37.000 --> 25:38.760
won't even light a lamp at night.

25:43.000 --> 25:44.920
If that's the case,

25:46.160 --> 25:49.920
we can look for houses
that should have lamps lit

25:50.680 --> 25:52.520
but are pitch black.

25:52.600 --> 25:54.800
That narrows down the search.

25:54.880 --> 25:56.960
Why are you so set on finding him, though?

25:57.040 --> 25:59.040
Just to get even for Ms. Yu?

26:01.160 --> 26:03.400
You wouldn't understand. That man…

26:05.760 --> 26:07.520
might be connected to something huge.

26:08.400 --> 26:10.880
He once showed me a tiger tally.

26:10.960 --> 26:13.000
Said it had something to do
with the Jinzhou tragedy.

26:13.080 --> 26:14.440
It's connected to Jinzhou?

26:18.080 --> 26:20.080
Then Yan Zheng must really
want to catch him

26:20.160 --> 26:21.400
and get some answers.

26:22.600 --> 26:25.680
Take my token. Tell them
there's an operation tonight.

26:25.760 --> 26:27.360
Good training for our squad.

26:28.720 --> 26:29.600
Got it.

27:01.720 --> 27:03.360
-Someone's inside. Circle around.
-Okay.

27:10.440 --> 27:13.600
GRACE IN HEART, PURITY IN FORM

27:30.240 --> 27:33.160
Throat's been cut.
Looks like he's been dead a while.

27:34.360 --> 27:35.760
How did he die?

27:38.160 --> 27:40.680
Keep searching.
See if he has a tiger tally on him.

27:41.800 --> 27:42.840
What tiger?

27:43.520 --> 27:45.840
The tiger tally, like in the operas.
Just search him.

27:45.920 --> 27:46.840
Okay.

28:16.920 --> 28:18.840
Captain Fan Changyu
pays her respects to the Marquis.

28:21.360 --> 28:24.200
Jin Changsheng pays his respects
to Prince Consort.

28:25.360 --> 28:27.680
One more word and you're transferred
to the kitchen brigade.

28:28.840 --> 28:30.040
Yes, Prince Consort.

28:30.760 --> 28:32.840
I'm going, Prince Consort.

28:43.520 --> 28:44.680
Sui Yuanhuai is dead.

28:45.800 --> 28:48.240
That trail… is gone cold.

29:01.440 --> 29:03.400
Sui Yuanhuai just died like that?

29:13.600 --> 29:15.120
Looks a lot like Sui Yuanhuai.

29:17.480 --> 29:18.560
All the evidence

29:19.320 --> 29:21.200
points to him being dead.

29:22.360 --> 29:24.440
But the more proof we have,
the more suspicious it gets.

29:25.160 --> 29:26.960
Have Zhao Xun
come identify him personally.

29:27.480 --> 29:28.880
Either way,

29:28.960 --> 29:31.360
in this world,
Sui Yuanhuai no longer exists.

29:40.440 --> 29:42.520
For years, there have been rumors

29:42.600 --> 29:45.160
that Wei Yan held the tiger tally
by imperial order, seeking reinforcements

29:45.240 --> 29:46.640
to break the siege at Jinzhou.

29:47.240 --> 29:49.880
But on the way,
he suddenly turned back to the capital,

29:49.960 --> 29:51.160
delaying the rescue.

29:53.720 --> 29:56.760
Back then, Wei Qilin was transporting
grain but suddenly diverted to Chongzhou.

29:57.560 --> 29:59.200
Wei Yan must have ordered him
to use the tiger tally

29:59.280 --> 30:00.480
to mobilize troops there.

30:02.320 --> 30:03.560
Yet in the end,

30:03.640 --> 30:05.400
Prince Changxin never sent troops,

30:05.480 --> 30:06.840
and the grain was delayed,

30:07.480 --> 30:08.760
and no one knows why.

30:15.120 --> 30:17.640
If Prince Changxin
saw the tiger tally back then

30:17.720 --> 30:19.800
but claimed it was fake
and refused to send troops…

30:22.200 --> 30:25.640
That would mean
Wei Qilin was truly wronged.

30:27.920 --> 30:28.920
Seems like…

30:30.680 --> 30:33.040
we're getting closer to the truth

30:34.080 --> 30:35.120
about the Jinzhou tragedy.

30:35.720 --> 30:37.720
If only we could find that tiger tally.

30:38.480 --> 30:40.480
I searched Prince Changxin's belongings,

30:40.560 --> 30:42.840
even Sui Yuanqing's personal belongings.

30:42.920 --> 30:43.920
Nothing.

30:44.000 --> 30:45.200
That Sui Yuanqing

30:45.280 --> 30:47.800
would rather be tortured
than tell us where the tally is.

30:47.880 --> 30:49.480
He even had the nerve to mock me.

30:50.080 --> 30:52.320
I should've let Mrs. Fan
cut him down with one blow.

30:59.720 --> 31:00.560
Marquis,

31:01.720 --> 31:03.560
Zhao Xun has examined the body.

31:03.640 --> 31:04.480
As you suspected,

31:04.560 --> 31:06.440
the dead man isn't Sui Yuanhuai.

31:06.520 --> 31:08.160
It's a double raised by Nanny Lan.

31:09.280 --> 31:10.680
Not only does this double look like him,

31:11.280 --> 31:14.000
every single burn scar on his body
was meticulously replicated.

31:14.680 --> 31:17.520
And the woman who died in the manor,
has her identity been confirmed?

31:18.200 --> 31:19.360
Zhao Xun identified her.

31:19.440 --> 31:20.640
It's indeed Princess Changxin.

31:25.440 --> 31:28.440
Killed his own foster mother
just to save himself.

31:29.600 --> 31:32.160
To catch Sui Yuanhuai… No,

31:32.960 --> 31:34.600
time to call him by his real name.

31:36.040 --> 31:37.400
To catch Qi Min,

31:37.920 --> 31:39.640
we'll need other leads.

31:40.400 --> 31:41.240
Anything else?

31:43.360 --> 31:44.600
All leads are dead ends.

31:45.520 --> 31:46.800
Strange thing is,

31:46.880 --> 31:48.360
every time we close in,

31:48.440 --> 31:50.000
it's like they're ready for us.

31:50.720 --> 31:53.840
I suspect
he's got eyes inside the command.

32:00.160 --> 32:03.000
Looks like someone's being used as a pawn,

32:03.080 --> 32:05.120
and they still think
they're fighting for justice.

32:06.800 --> 32:09.000
Marquis, what's our next move?

32:11.160 --> 32:12.760
Take Zhao Xun to see Sui Yuanqing.

32:13.280 --> 32:15.960
Bring him the news of
Princess Changxin's death.

32:17.920 --> 32:19.880
First squad, left. Second squad, right.

32:20.640 --> 32:22.080
Spread out in a fan formation.

32:22.160 --> 32:23.000
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

32:23.520 --> 32:24.640
Check the bushes and rocks.

32:24.720 --> 32:27.320
Copy that.Turn everything over.
Leave no spot untouched.

32:27.400 --> 32:28.560
-Let's move.
-Check over there.

32:30.040 --> 32:31.520
Nothing here.

32:31.600 --> 32:32.680
Over there.

32:32.760 --> 32:33.600
Follow me.

32:36.800 --> 32:38.760
Master, it's the Xie army.

32:41.880 --> 32:43.640
Sui Yuanqing wasn't enough.

32:44.760 --> 32:46.200
Looks like the Marquis

32:46.720 --> 32:49.240
won't stop until he has my head.

32:50.560 --> 32:51.880
How's Madam's whereabouts?

32:52.720 --> 32:54.040
No sign of her yet.

33:03.280 --> 33:06.160
Master, the Li family took plenty from us,

33:06.240 --> 33:08.120
and still no sign of their support.

33:08.200 --> 33:10.240
They're letting the Marquis hunt us down.

33:10.320 --> 33:11.760
You don't think they've turned on us?

33:13.840 --> 33:15.520
If the Li family had turned,

33:15.600 --> 33:17.280
we'd have been captured long ago.

33:18.760 --> 33:21.640
But for being grandfather and grandson,

33:22.880 --> 33:27.040
Grand Tutor Li and Li Huai'an
really aren't on the same page.

33:33.840 --> 33:35.160
Almost time now.

33:35.240 --> 33:36.240
He should be here soon,

33:37.080 --> 33:38.800
if he believed me.

33:43.160 --> 33:44.040
Master.

33:52.920 --> 33:54.560
With Grand Tutor Li's help,

33:55.080 --> 33:57.080
I'm most pleased.

34:34.520 --> 34:36.719
-I need to tell you something.
-I don't want to hear it.

34:36.800 --> 34:38.120
I just want you to know.

34:40.239 --> 34:42.239
Anyone in this world
can be a prince consort.

34:43.080 --> 34:44.280
But I, Xie Zheng, will not.

34:46.520 --> 34:48.239
I already married into your family.

34:48.760 --> 34:50.639
I belong only to Fan Changyu.

34:52.320 --> 34:53.520
For this lifetime,

34:54.960 --> 34:56.199
my heart is yours alone.

35:20.560 --> 35:21.440
You…

35:25.280 --> 35:26.920
Can you stop being so good to me?

35:27.960 --> 35:29.200
The kinder you are,

35:30.880 --> 35:31.880
the more uneasy I feel.

35:33.880 --> 35:35.520
Is it because of who you are?

35:37.800 --> 35:38.920
You know?

35:46.560 --> 35:47.840
I saw that letter.

35:48.680 --> 35:50.040
I know he was your father.

35:51.600 --> 35:53.120
I also know what you're afraid of.

35:54.680 --> 35:56.280
But I want you to know.

35:57.120 --> 35:58.800
I'll keep investigating,

35:59.960 --> 36:01.240
until I find the truth.

36:03.400 --> 36:04.720
And on this path,

36:06.080 --> 36:07.160
I want to be by your side.

36:21.280 --> 36:22.800
But Sui Yuanhuai is dead.

36:23.640 --> 36:27.200
What if the truth isn't what we think?

36:35.640 --> 36:36.760
That's the second thing

36:37.720 --> 36:38.960
I wanted to tell you.

36:39.800 --> 36:40.960
I'm planning

36:43.160 --> 36:44.200
to release Sui Yuanqing.

36:45.000 --> 36:45.960
What?

37:02.680 --> 37:04.520
-You may go.
-Yes.

37:09.520 --> 37:10.360
Young Heir.

37:11.400 --> 37:13.040
Zhao Xun.

37:13.120 --> 37:14.760
You traitor!

37:14.840 --> 37:16.400
You betrayed my big brother!

37:18.240 --> 37:19.120
Young Heir.

37:19.880 --> 37:21.960
It was your brother who betrayed you.

37:25.640 --> 37:26.880
A traitor.

37:28.160 --> 37:30.320
Seeing that my big brother
has already escaped,

37:31.040 --> 37:32.720
you want to coax
a confession for the Marquis

37:33.600 --> 37:35.720
and drive a wedge between us brothers.

37:36.520 --> 37:38.480
Save your breath.

37:39.400 --> 37:41.120
Even if I can't kill you today,

37:43.080 --> 37:45.520
my brother will avenge me soon enough.

37:47.560 --> 37:51.200
And Princess Changxin's death,
who will avenge her?

37:56.040 --> 37:57.200
Mother is dead?

38:02.040 --> 38:03.640
Marquis of Wu'an!

38:04.160 --> 38:05.600
Some hero you are,

38:05.680 --> 38:08.280
laying hands on a woman!

38:08.880 --> 38:11.320
The one who killed the princess
wasn't the Marquis of Wu'an.

38:11.400 --> 38:12.600
It was Sui Yuanhuai.

38:13.200 --> 38:14.040
No.

38:14.600 --> 38:16.520
We should call him Qi Min.

38:19.960 --> 38:21.280
Who?

38:21.360 --> 38:22.520
All these years,

38:23.040 --> 38:24.800
your dear elder brother,

38:24.880 --> 38:26.320
he isn't Sui Yuanhuai.

38:26.840 --> 38:28.160
He's Qi Min,

38:28.760 --> 38:32.560
the former Eastern Palace grandson,
killed by Prince Changxin.

38:33.320 --> 38:34.800
The real Sui Yuanhuai

38:34.880 --> 38:37.000
died 17 years ago,

38:37.080 --> 38:39.120
in that fire at the Eastern Palace.

38:47.840 --> 38:48.760
No.

38:51.840 --> 38:52.760
Impossible.

38:56.600 --> 39:00.000
You're just using me
to go after my brother.

39:01.040 --> 39:02.200
Young Heir,

39:02.920 --> 39:04.120
wake up.

39:05.160 --> 39:08.880
Qi Min killed the princess
to fake his own death and escape.

39:12.120 --> 39:14.960
He's already reclaimed his identity
as the imperial grandson.

39:15.760 --> 39:19.440
He's Qi Min, the one who destroyed your
family and left Changxin Manor in ruins.

39:23.920 --> 39:24.760
No…

39:26.120 --> 39:27.200
It's not like that.

39:28.320 --> 39:29.440
It's not like that.

39:32.840 --> 39:34.920
Aren't you my brother's lackey?

39:36.080 --> 39:37.480
Why are you telling me this?

39:38.080 --> 39:39.080
That's right.

39:39.920 --> 39:41.960
I used to follow Qi Min,

39:42.960 --> 39:44.840
but that was for the sake
of the true imperial line.

39:46.040 --> 39:47.960
He is brutal in his nature.

39:48.040 --> 39:49.760
He's unfit to inherit the throne.

39:50.840 --> 39:52.120
I was forced

39:53.560 --> 39:54.800
to turn to the Marquis of Wu'an.

40:06.200 --> 40:07.720
Sui Yuanhuai…

40:08.640 --> 40:09.600
No…

40:10.280 --> 40:11.800
Qi Min.

40:12.400 --> 40:14.480
I'll tear you limb from limb.

40:15.000 --> 40:17.320
Avenge my father and mother!

40:20.760 --> 40:21.720
Young Heir.

40:22.680 --> 40:23.800
I can let you go.

40:25.240 --> 40:26.200
Let me go?

40:27.240 --> 40:28.120
Why?

40:28.200 --> 40:29.800
My mother, Nanny Lan,

40:30.880 --> 40:32.440
raised Qi Min for years

40:33.200 --> 40:34.640
and died by his hand.

40:36.800 --> 40:39.000
I only regret I'm not strong enough.

40:39.080 --> 40:40.960
If you can eliminate Qi Min,

40:41.480 --> 40:43.800
both our vendettas will be settled.

40:51.760 --> 40:53.920
You're nothing but a lackey.

40:58.160 --> 40:59.760
But if you let me go,

41:01.400 --> 41:03.360
I'll give you what you want.

41:12.760 --> 41:14.640
Young Heir, this way.

41:24.240 --> 41:27.280
You really think he can find Qi Min?

41:29.760 --> 41:31.720
They've been brothers all these years.

41:32.240 --> 41:33.480
He'll find a way.

41:34.840 --> 41:37.480
19TH DAY, 7TH MONTH
17TH YEAR OF ZHENGPING

41:49.080 --> 41:51.000
Sui Yuanqing escaped from prison.

41:52.040 --> 41:52.920
What?

41:57.280 --> 42:00.040
Get this to the post officer.
Send it to the capital now. No delays.

42:00.120 --> 42:00.960
Yes, sir.

42:15.960 --> 42:18.320
YAMEN

45:00.600 --> 45:03.680
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

45:03.760 --> 45:04.680
Subtitle translation by: Wanjiao Song
